---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---
<Base title="Book your free Scout strategy call" description="Tell Scout what you are targeting and meet the team before choosing a Human Assistant plan.">
<section class="bg-brand-950 py-12 text-white sm:py-20"><div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-5"><div class="grid gap-10 lg:grid-cols-[0.8fr_1.2fr] lg:items-start"><div class="lg:sticky lg:top-28"><a href="/" class="text-sm font-bold text-brand-300">← Back to Scout</a><h1 class="mt-8 font-display text-5xl font-extrabold leading-tight text-white sm:text-7xl">Let us understand the search before we assign your assistant.</h1><p class="mt-6 max-w-xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-white/70">In 15 minutes, we will learn what you are targeting, explain the Human Assistant workflow, and help you choose the right plan.</p><div class="mt-9 space-y-4 text-sm font-bold text-white/75"><p>✓ No commitment or sales pressure</p><p>✓ Bring your resume if you have one</p><p>✓ Leave with a clearer application plan</p></div></div><form class="rounded-2xl bg-white p-6 text-ink sm:p-8"><h2 class="text-2xl font-extrabold">Book a free strategy call</h2><p class="mt-2 text-ink-soft">We will use these details to make the call useful.</p><div class="mt-7 grid gap-5 sm:grid-cols-2"><label class="text-sm font-bold">First name<input required class="mt-2 w-full rounded-xl border border-ink/15 px-4 py-3"></label><label class="text-sm font-bold">Last name<input required class="mt-2 w-full rounded-xl border border-ink/15 px-4 py-3"></label><label class="text-sm font-bold sm:col-span-2">Email<input type="email" required class="mt-2 w-full rounded-xl border border-ink/15 px-4 py-3"></label><label class="text-sm font-bold">Primary role<select class="mt-2 w-full rounded-xl border border-ink/15 px-4 py-3"><option>Select a role family</option><option>Engineering</option><option>Product</option><option>Operations</option><option>Sales & marketing</option><option>Other</option></select></label><label class="text-sm font-bold">Target location<input placeholder="Remote, London, New York…" class="mt-2 w-full rounded-xl border border-ink/15 px-4 py-3"></label><label class="text-sm font-bold sm:col-span-2">What is hardest about applying right now?<textarea rows="4" class="mt-2 w-full rounded-xl border border-ink/15 px-4 py-3"></textarea></label></div><div class="mt-7 rounded-xl bg-surface p-4"><strong class="text-sm">Next: choose a time</strong><p class="mt-1 text-sm text-ink-soft">Connect Calendly or your scheduling provider to this button before launch.</p></div><button class="mt-5 w-full rounded-full bg-brand-500 px-6 py-3.5 font-extrabold">Continue to available times</button><p class="mt-4 text-center text-xs text-ink-muted">Prefer to start without a call? <a href="/login" class="font-bold text-brand-700">Create an account</a></p></form></div></div></section>
</Base>
